Merge pull request #81 from gene1wood/dont_block_on_failure

Don't block processing other bugs when casa_set_status fails

Don't block processing other bugs when casa_set_status fails

Previously if any bug got a non-200 response from CAS when
setting the status, the tool would throw an uncaught exception
and not process subsequent bugs.

This instead logs the error and continues
